Exercise 1: Type the following commands
>>> print ("Hello, world!")
Hello, world!
>>> print ("Hello", "world!")
Hello world!
>>> print(3)
3
>>> print(3.0)
3.0
>>> print(2+5)
7
>>> print(2.0 + 3.0)
5.0
>>> print("2" + "3")
23
>>> print("2 + 3 =", 2+3)
2 + 3 = 5
>>> print(2*3)
6
>>> print(2**3)
8
>>> print(7/3)
2.3333333333333335
>>> print(7//3)
2
